## Data Sources

This repository redistributes Japanese tax primary sources from the following agencies.
Each data item is governed by the public data license of its original publisher.

- National Tax Agency (NTA, 国税庁) — https://www.nta.go.jp
  - Tax Answers (タックスアンサー)
  - Circulars (通達)
  - Q&A Cases (質疑応答事例)
  - Written Answers (文書回答事例)
  - License: 公共データ利用規約 第1.0版

- National Tax Tribunal (国税不服審判所) — https://www.kfs.go.jp
  - Saiketsu (裁決事例)
  - License: 公共データ利用規約 第1.0版

- e-Gov Law Database (e-Gov 法令データ検索) — https://elaws.e-gov.go.jp
  - Law text fetched on-demand via e-Gov Law API v2
  - License: 公共データ利用規約 第1.0版

Individual data items include `canonical_url` and `license` metadata in their frontmatter.
